whereby to prove; that the said Mr. (^Oates^) , and Mr. (^Bedlow^)   #
in this Examinants
hearing should say,$] (^Come let us contrive a story to ruine the    #
Lord Treasurer^) , 
[$and that Mr. (^Bedlow^) should within a day or two after come to   #
